snippet.title: Plants vs. Zombies: Garden Warfare - Official E3 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: The first official trailer for Plants vs. Zombies™ Garden Warfare. The ultimate battle for brainz — coming exclusively first to Xbox One and Xbox 360 followed by PC and other platforms. Visit www.PlantsvsZombies.com/GW to go behind the scenes and sign up for insider updates.
